NK079(dzu)002:1330: ye shes nyid kyang sgyu ma yin phyir gsog /rang
NK079(dzu)002:1331: snang bsod nams ye shes de nyid 'jig rten 'das
NK079(dzu)002:1333: rgyal ba gzugs sku mngon 'byung skyob dang byin rlabs ston pa yang //
NK079(dzu)002:1334: rang sems rnam pa yin te gud na yang //
NK079(dzu)002:1335: rang snang sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor bya ba byed nus la //
NK079(dzu)002:1336: gzi byin byin rlabs 'gro la phan 'dog pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1337: de bzhin nyid las mi gnyis 'dus byas pa'ang //
NK079(dzu)002:1338: mdor na rang snang sems nyid de bzhin yin phyir ro //
NK079(dzu)002:1339: sems nyid snang ba kun kyang rdo rje 'dus ma byas su mkhas pas bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1340: sgrub pa'i yan lag cho ga rnam lnga rdzogs par bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1341: dang po stong pa byang chub gnyis pa snying rje chen po yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1342: gsum pa yi ge bzhi pa la ni dam tshig rgya //
NK079(dzu)002:1343: lnga pa la ni gzugs rdzogs gzugs ldan yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1344: yo byad gnas mchog yid 'ong gdan mchog nyi zla pad sogs dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1345: phyag mtshan rdo rje dril bu gzungs ma mtshan ldan dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1346: a mri ta sogs phyi nang 'byor pa'i yo byad dang ldan bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1347: snying gar ye shes sems dpa' bsgom de'i snying gar nyi zla'i dkyil //
NK079(dzu)002:1348: dam tshig phyag rgya bzhag ste de steng yig 'bru
NK079(dzu)002:1349: bzhag /bzla tshe spro bsdus bzlas pa'i yan lag yin
NK079(dzu)002:1350: // bco lnga ldan zhing ma nyams bsgrub la brtson na 'grub //
NK079(dzu)002:1351: dus ni zla ba drug dang bcu gnyis bcu bzhi bcu drug gis //
NK079(dzu)002:1352: tshe la dbang sogs rig 'dzin rab 'bring tha ma 'grub //
NK079(dzu)002:1353: 'bras bu tshe dbang rig 'dzin de nyid kyis //
NK079(dzu)002:1354: tshe lo bcu drug gis ni sku lnga lhun gyis grub //
NK079(dzu)002:1355: de ltar rig 'dzin khyad par de dag kyang //
NK079(dzu)002:1356: ye shes nyid la nyid snang bsam yas mchog /zhing khams mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo na //
NK079(dzu)002:1357: sprul pa bsam yas zhal mthong dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1358: mnyes nas chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1359: rig 'dzin rtsal gyii khyad par de nyid kyang //
NK079(dzu)002:1360: tshogs gnyis mthun te ye shes rang snang ba'o //
NK079(dzu)002:1361: gcig dang du ma bral ba'i mtha' 'das de bzhin nyid //
NK079(dzu)002:1362: rgyal bas kyang ni gzigs pa ma yin te //
NK079(dzu)002:1363: rang byung ye shes nyid la mi gnas tshul tsam snang bar zad //
NK079(dzu)002:1364: log par rtog pas brtags pa kun kyang ye nas rnam med cing //
NK079(dzu)002:1365: rang snang ye shes dbyings dang de bzhin nyid las gud na yod ma yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1366: de phyir thugs rje chen pos 'brel ba yi //
NK079(dzu)002:1367: 'gro drug dus gnas mun sel snang //
NK079(dzu)002:1368: des na 'bras bu rang snang dkyil 'khor nyid du chos kun 'byung bar des //
NK079(dzu)002:1369: don dam dkyil 'khor nyid ni stangs dpyal gnyis sam bcu //
NK079(dzu)002:1370: gsal byas dad pas zhugs na dngos grub yid 'ong mnyam par 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)002:1371: me tog dor te skal mnyam ye shes gang gnyer ba //
NK079(dzu)002:1372: gang nyer ya mtshan dngos grub 'byung bar nges //
NK079(dzu)002:1373: bco lnga mi ldan dam med dam tshig nyes na brlag par gyur ta re //
NK079(dzu)002:1374: mi 'grub bgegs su 'gyur zhes rgyal bas gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1375: rdo rje dam tshig bkod po'i le'u ste dgu pa'o
NK079(dzu)002:1376: ////de nas dgyes chen rgyal po'i sprin la snyoms zhugs
NK079(dzu)002:1377: te // dbang mchog sbyin pa 'di nyid 'gro ba'i ched du brjod //
NK079(dzu)002:1378: spyi dang khyad par ma thob skyon dang rdzas dang 'bras bu lnga'o //
NK079(dzu)002:1379: spyir ni yab yum phyag rgyar bsgoms te sbyor ba las //
NK079(dzu)002:1380: bde mchog yig 'bru'i tshogs su rdo rje'i lam nas mkha' la 'khyiil //
NK079(dzu)002:1381: rdo rje'i rtse nas gnas su bstim zhing so so'i dkyil 'khor bsgyur //
NK079(dzu)002:1382: so so nyan dang bsgrub dang las 'chad slob dpon nyid dang lnga'o //
NK079(dzu)002:1383: nyan pa rna bar sems spros gzhal yas gdan dang bcas //
NK079(dzu)002:1384: t+r+aa gnyis la ni rin chen phyag rgya'i sku gyur gsal spro thim //
NK079(dzu)002:1385: gsang gsum mnyan cha mi smra tshig bshad bsgrags //
NK079(dzu)002:1386: bsgrub pa snying gar de bzhin sgyu 'phrul dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK079(dzu)002:1387: rdo rje gzungs dang mchod dang sbyor dang tshig bshad bsgrags //
NK079(dzu)002:1388: las ni lag par de bzhin las rigs spro bstim bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1389: las dang pho nya byed par bka' yis rab tu bsgrags //
NK079(dzu)002:1390: 'chad pa lce la pad+ma'i rigs yin te //
NK079(dzu)002:1391: snod mthun gsang ba bsgrag pa'i tshig bshad brjod //
NK079(dzu)002:1392: slob dpon yan lag lnga la zhi khro'i tshom bu lngas /
NK079(dzu)002:1393: dkyil 'khor byed dang dbang sbyin ces par bka' yis bsgrags //
NK079(dzu)002:1394: skyon ni bla ma ma mnyes lnga po ma thob par //
NK079(dzu)002:1395: lnga por rtsom pas dngos grub mi thob brlag par nges //
NK079(dzu)002:1396: de rus rdzas kyi rnam pa dgos pa yang //
NK079(dzu)002:1397: chos kyi rgyal mtshan thob phyir rigs lnga'i dbu rgyan sbyin //
NK079(dzu)002:1398: shes byar ma rmongs sna tshogs dar gyi cod pan te //
NK079(dzu)002:1399: gzungs dang ting 'dzin me tog phreng ba btag /gzhan gyi mi thub brgya phrag go cha bskon //
NK079(dzu)002:1400: bdun las rgyal ba'i chu srin rgyal mtshan gtad //
NK079(dzu)002:1401: mi 'da' mi shigs rigs kyi phyag rgyas btab //
NK079(dzu)002:1402: tsha gdung sel phyir skyob pa gdugs kyis dgab //
NK079(dzu)002:1403: bag chags sbyang phyir lnga'i bum pa bsten //
NK079(dzu)002:1404: 'dod pa'i yon tan longs spyod bza' btung bstab //
NK079(dzu)002:1405: nges pa'i 'bras bu smin phyir snying po lnga //
NK079(dzu)002:1406: 'di dag rdzas su sbyin ces rgyal bas gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1407: 'bras bu rgyal sras ngan song med pa dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1408: 'jig rten tshe dang bde ba thob pa dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1409: mtho ris lha mi thar pa'i chos kyi rgyal por 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)002:1410: dbang sbyin pa'i le'u ste bcu pa'o ////de nas bcom ldan 'das dgyes pa chen pos //
NK079(dzu)002:1411: rgyal po'i tshogs su dbang bskur mnyam bzhag ste //
NK079(dzu)002:1412: bde ba mchog gi le'u 'di 'gro ba ched du brjod //
NK079(dzu)002:1413: rnal 'byor dgongs pa'i khyad par dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1414: byin rlabs bya dang sbyor sgrol dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1416: zhi khro tshom bu'i grangs bstan pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1417: rnam pa drug gis yang dag bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1418: dgongs pa rgyu gcig yig 'bru byin rlabs mngon sum rtogs rnam bzhi //
NK079(dzu)002:1419: rgyu gcig don dam kun rdzob dbyer med pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1420: ma skyes sgyu ma snang dang rang bzhin med par
NK079(dzu)002:1421: gcig /a o +amo ste sku gsung thugs rang bzhin
NK079(dzu)002:1422: // ma skyes sgyu ma dbyer med yig 'bru'i tshul //
NK079(dzu)002:1423: ras dkar dmar po'i tshon gyis bsgyur tshul du //
NK079(dzu)002:1424: rgyu gcig yig 'brus chos kun byin gyis rlob //
NK079(dzu)002:1425: lung dang man ngan mi bsten mi 'gal bar //
NK079(dzu)002:1426: rang rig blo yis mngon sum rtogs zhes bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1427: rtogs bzhis chos kun mngon rdzogs rgyal po che //
NK079(dzu)002:1428: gang zhig de rtogs tshogs kyi bdag por gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1429: rdzogs chen rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor zhes kyang de la bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1430: ji ltar yan lag lnga dbang po //
NK079(dzu)002:1431: ye shes lngas bsdus rnam min du bsgom //
NK079(dzu)002:1432: zhi khro rgyal ba yab yum byin gyis brlabs //
NK079(dzu)002:1433: 'dod yon lnga sogs yul gyi rnam pa kun //
NK079(dzu)002:1434: rnam pa ma yin yi ge m+au du bsgom //
NK079(dzu)002:1435: zhi khro dbyings phyug yum du bsgom par bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1436: gos rgyan bza' btung glu tshig bro gar sprin tshogs kun //
NK079(dzu)002:1437: byang chub sems tshogs yi ge h'u du rab bsgoms te //
NK079(dzu)002:1438: spyad na dngos grub 'byung ba'i dkyil 'khor mnyes //
NK079(dzu)002:1439: m+au h'u nyid sku gsung thugs nyid byin rlabs bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1440: sbyor ba'i gzungs ma lha klu'i bu mo'am rigs ngan sogs //
NK079(dzu)002:1441: zhi rgyas dag la dbye ba'am dbang drag dag la mi dbye bar //
NK079(dzu)002:1442: bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhi'i rim pa rab tu brtsam //
NK079(dzu)002:1443: bsnyen pa don dam byang chub sems shes yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1444: nye ba'i bsnyen pa bdag nyid phyag rgyar bsgom //
NK079(dzu)002:1445: sgrub pa yum nyid gzungs su byin brlab bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1446: sgrub chen yab yum gnyis med byin brlabs la //
NK079(dzu)002:1447: mkha' las sems 'phros bdag mchod rgyal ba mnyes //
NK079(dzu)002:1448: 'gro tshim nyi zla lce yis dngos zos na //
NK079(dzu)002:1449: nam mkha' 'gro dang mdog bzang tshe ring ba //
NK079(dzu)002:1450: thun mong mchog gi grub pa yid bzhin bdag por 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)002:1451: bsgral ba'i zhing gyur rgyu mchog rnam lnga pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1452: a 'bras rgun 'brum pa na se dang ge rgyas a ga ru //
NK079(dzu)002:1453: mchog phran gzhan yang mchog gis bsdus pa bstan //
NK079(dzu)002:1454: blo ngan 'jig rten zhes su bde gshegs gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1455: mkhas pas e las nyi zla'i steng du bzhag /gtsug tu ye shes sems dpa' ngan song sbyong //
NK079(dzu)002:1456: che ba'i nga rgyal bskyed cing sor mo 'bru bcu bsgom //
NK079(dzu)002:1457: 'bru bcu'i 'od kyis rnam shes bsregs nas h'u du
NK079(dzu)002:1458: dag /h'u nyid mkha' la thim par 'phangs te phyag
NK079(dzu)002:1459: rgyar bsgyur // de las sku gsal 'od 'phros rgyan dang ldan //
NK079(dzu)002:1460: gnyis su med par bsgral zhes de la bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1461: don dam skye med kun rdzob mig yor tshul //
NK079(dzu)002:1462: sbyor sgrol byas kyang rdul tsam byas mi dmigs //
NK079(dzu)002:1463: 'jug pa 'bras bcas dag mnyam gsum dang bzhi //
NK079(dzu)002:1464: snod ni 'byung lnga gzhal yas yum du dag /phung
NK079(dzu)002:1465: po bcud rnams rgyal ba yab tu dag /tshogs brgyad
NK079(dzu)002:1466: sems dag ye shes lngar dag rtog /de tshe don
NK079(dzu)002:1467: dam ma skyes dbyings su mnyam //
NK079(dzu)002:1468: kun rdzob sgyu ma phyag rgya chen por mnyam //
NK079(dzu)002:1469: shes rig lha dang yul rnams lha mor mnyam //
NK079(dzu)002:1470: des na thams cad dkyil 'khor kun tu bzang po'i zhing //
NK079(dzu)002:1471: byed spyod nyid kyang tshogs gnyis rdzogs par rol //
NK079(dzu)002:1472: de phyir rang bzhin lhun grub tshogs zhes gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1473: bkri drang tshogs de dkyil 'khor byed pa'i tshe //
NK079(dzu)002:1474: yan lag lnga po ma nyams yo byad rnam lngar ldan //
NK079(dzu)002:1475: cho ga lnga rdzogs tshogs 'dus dkyil 'khor kyis //
NK079(dzu)002:1476: nges par legs pa'i dngos grub dgongs pa 'grub //
NK079(dzu)002:1477: tshom bu'i grangs kyang lnga dang gsum dang gcig /rigs lnga rigs gsum rigs gcig tshom bu la //
NK079(dzu)002:1478: khro bo khro mo nyi shu'i 'khor lo bskor //
NK079(dzu)002:1479: tshom bu de kun gtso gzungs zung du 'khril //
NK079(dzu)002:1480: khro bo'i tshom bu grangs kyang de bzhin te //
NK079(dzu)002:1481: pho nya phyag brnyan bka' nyan ci bgyi rnams //
NK079(dzu)002:1482: 'khor bar dngos grub las rnams rdzogs par byed //
NK079(dzu)002:1483: tshogs kyi le'u ste bcu gcig pa'o ////de nas rgyal po dgyes chen pos //
NK079(dzu)002:1484: rol mo sprin 'phro rgyan bkod snyoms zhugs te //
NK079(dzu)002:1485: tshogs sgrub le'u 'di 'gro ba'i ched du brjod //
NK079(dzu)002:1486: longs spyod so sor 'grub pa'i khyad par dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1487: rig 'dzin phyi dang rigs kyi rnal 'byor dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1488: 'bras bu'i khyad par gegs med khyad lnga'o //
NK079(dzu)002:1489: so so'i sgyu 'phrul brtan pa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK079(dzu)002:1490: phyag rgya'i dngos grub rnam pa lnga //
NK079(dzu)002:1491: lhun gyis grub par bde gshegs rgyal bas gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1492: rig 'dzin shes 'jug 'bras bu khyad par bsam yas pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1493: rtogs gzhi'i tshul rig shes pa'i mtshan nyid yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1494: yang dang yang du goms pa 'jug pa ste //
NK079(dzu)002:1495: goms mthus mngon du gyur pa 'bras bu'i mtshan nyid yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1496: rgyu rkyen 'bras bu nus mthu gang gyur pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1497: rig 'dzin zhes su rgyal ba'i zhing du grags //
NK079(dzu)002:1498: 'dod khams lha mi tshangs pa'i skye gnas su //
NK079(dzu)002:1499: skye gzhi rnam par dag pa 'dzin mod kyi //
NK079(dzu)002:1500: rtogs pa'i khyad par sa la gnas 'gyur yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1501: byang chub sa bcu bde gshegs pa gsum ste //
NK079(dzu)002:1502: de nyid dus ni pha rol phyin bcu byang chub pa yi rgyu //
NK079(dzu)002:1503: sbyin sogs rab dga' la sogs lhun gyis grub //
NK079(dzu)002:1504: thabs kyi kun tu 'od yin shes rab pad+ma can //
NK079(dzu)002:1505: thabs dang shes rab sa mchog 'khor lo tshogs chen te //
NK079(dzu)002:1506: rgyu 'bras rim don ma yin lhun gyis grub //
NK079(dzu)002:1507: khyad par sa zhes lhun grub nyid la brjod //
NK079(dzu)002:1508: rigs kyi rnal 'byor rdo rje sems dpa' nyid //
NK079(dzu)002:1509: stangs dpyal mkha' dbyings nyi zla'i steng bsgom na //
NK079(dzu)002:1510: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus bsgom par 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)002:1511: de phyir rigs kyi rigs zhes brjod pa yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1512: phyogs dus kun nas sangs rgyas btsal kyang mi rnyed de //
NK079(dzu)002:1513: rang rig sems nyid rdzogs sangs rgyas kyi dkyil 'khor yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1514: de phyir sems las ma gtogs sangs rgyas gzhan du
NK079(dzu)002:1515: ma 'tshal cig /rang sems rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor kun
NK079(dzu)002:1517: de phyir dkyil 'khor thams cad 'grub par 'gyur zhes rgyal bas gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1518: rang sems dkyil 'khor nyid du rtogs chub na //
NK079(dzu)002:1519: cho ga lhag chad skyon man gegs med yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1520: de skad brjod tshe rol mos bde gshegs mnyes //
NK079(dzu)002:1521: tshogs sgrub pa'i le'u ste bcu gnyis pa'o ////de nas bde gshegs kun kyang gcig tu dgongs 'dus na //
NK079(dzu)002:1522: lhun grub dam tshig snying po'i sprin la snyoms zhugs nas //
NK079(dzu)002:1523: mdor bsdus gsang ba 'di nyid 'gro ba'i ched du brjod //
NK079(dzu)002:1524: gsang ba'i spyi dang mdo dang rgyas dang mos pa'i yon tan dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1525: rnyed dka' lam gyur gtad dang skyon dang rnam pa brgyad //
NK079(dzu)002:1526: spyi ni ma rtogs phyal pa rgyang 'phen dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1527: log par rtogs pa mur thug mu stegs dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1528: phyogs rtogs nyan thos rang rgyal rigs can dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1529: yang dag ma rtogs byang chub shes bya'i sgrib //
NK079(dzu)002:1530: 'dul ba'i las ni bya ba gnyi ga'i rgyud //
NK079(dzu)002:1531: dgongs pa'i don gsang phyi pa thub pa'i rgyud //
NK079(dzu)002:1532: rang bzhin sku gsung thugs gsang rgyud rnams kun //
NK079(dzu)002:1533: bkri phyir rang bzhin gsang don rgyas pa rnams //
NK079(dzu)002:1534: yi ge sgra btang tshogs 'brel ming tshogs la //
NK079(dzu)002:1535: brten pa'i tshig rnams kyis ni rab mtshon te //
NK079(dzu)002:1536: dgongs pa'i dbang gis don gnyis gab cing sbas //
NK079(dzu)002:1537: kun gyi khongs na gnas pa'i don de gsal bar 'di las 'byin mdzad pa'i //
NK079(dzu)002:1538: theg pa kun la mkhas pa ston pa'i thugs la gnas //
NK079(dzu)002:1539: de phyir gsang ba'i snying po de kho na //
NK079(dzu)002:1540: de nyid nges pa'i khongs nas phyung zhes ston pas gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1541: 'byung gnas gtan la pheb ces de nyid yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1542: sna tshogs don 'chang smra zhing ston ces de la bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1543: mdo don dkyil 'khor bcu gnyis bsdus bshad pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1544: dkyil 'khor de bzhin nyid ces bya bar shar //
NK079(dzu)002:1545: de bzhin nyid ldan rang bzhin dkyil 'khor gyis //
NK079(dzu)002:1546: gzugs brnyan lhag pa'i gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor la //
NK079(dzu)002:1547: ting 'dzin lhag pa'i ting 'dzin dkyil 'khor bsgom //
NK079(dzu)002:1548: tshogs chen bya ba dkyil 'khor nyid yin te //
NK079(dzu)002:1549: dkyil 'khor las byung thugs rjes 'dul bar bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1550: thugs ni byang chub rnam gnyis dkyil 'khor yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1551: lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor mchog tu gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1552: bcu gnyis nyid du rgyud kyi don rdzogs te //
NK079(dzu)002:1553: gsang ba'i man ngag ces kyang de phyir brjod //
NK079(dzu)002:1554: rgyas pa de bzhin nyid ni rtogs dka' gsang ba spros med thig le ste //
NK079(dzu)002:1555: dkyil 'khor kun 'byung zhes ni dbyings zhes gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1556: rang bzhin 'byung lnga dngos med shes rab yum //
NK079(dzu)002:1557: chen po rag pa thabs te yab lnga yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1558: gnyis med sems las sprul pa'i lha tshogs ni //
NK079(dzu)002:1559: dbang drug yul drug dus bzhi rig pa rnam pa
NK079(dzu)002:1560: drug /phyin ci ma log rang bzhin dkyil 'khor yin
NK079(dzu)002:1561: // rang bzhin kun tu bzang po'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK079(dzu)002:1562: thugs kyi ye shes lnga nyid byang chub sems yin te //
NK079(dzu)002:1563: rnal 'byor bdag nyid chen po'i byang chub sems //
NK079(dzu)002:1564: snying po'i thig ler chos kun mnyam sbyor lhag par bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1565: rnal 'byor bde ba'i tshogs mchog mi zad rol mo yis //
NK079(dzu)002:1566: ye shes dgyes pa'i lha la mchod 'bul tshogs zhes bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1567: zag med rang rig bsod nams rgyu nyid kyis //
NK079(dzu)002:1568: ye shes rang snang sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor rol mo
NK079(dzu)002:1569: mtha' yas mchog /de nyid ting nge 'dzin de lhag
NK079(dzu)002:1570: pa'i ting 'dzin gsang ba'i thig le yum gyi dbyings
NK079(dzu)002:1571: // thig le de nyid sangs rgyas kun gyi dngos gzhi yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1572: bde gshegs sku sogs bdag gi zhal mthong ba //
NK079(dzu)002:1573: rig pas dbang bsgyur dngos grub dam pa gzugs brnyan rnam gnyis yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1574: lhun grub dkyil 'khor la gnas dkyil 'khor ma lus shing //
NK079(dzu)002:1575: rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor nyid du ma lus lhun gyis grub //
NK079(dzu)002:1576: des na dkyil 'khor mi bzad rgyan du ma lus de dag bdag gis thogs /
NK079(dzu)002:1577: thugs rje rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor mnyam sbyor las //
NK079(dzu)002:1578: snying rje chen po'i dkyil 'khor 'khor mi zad yongs kyis 'byung //
NK079(dzu)002:1579: phyogs dus 'gro ba'i dkyil 'khor sprul pas 'dul pa yi //
NK079(dzu)002:1580: mgon po ji snyed sgyu ma'i dkyil 'khor thabs kyis sgrol ba yang //
NK079(dzu)002:1581: bya byed med par spyod pas 'dul ba'i dkyil 'khor yin par bde gshegs gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1582: zhes pa'i yon tan bcu gnyis shes rab gsum gyis mnyam sbyor bas //
NK079(dzu)002:1583: rang byung dkyil 'khor stod dam lhun gyis grub //
NK079(dzu)002:1584: 'di las rgyal rnams cis kyang 'da' bar ga la mdzad //
NK079(dzu)002:1585: gang zhig dkyil 'khor 'di dag kun la mos pa'i skyes bu la //
NK079(dzu)002:1586: phyogs dus rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus kun //
NK079(dzu)002:1587: sras kyi dam pa mchog tu dgongs par 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)002:1588: 'di ni rnyed dka' bskal pa rdul snyed sbyangs pas rnyed pa'o //
NK079(dzu)002:1589: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor ma lus bsnyen pa yi //
NK079(dzu)002:1590: 'bras bu gsang chen nges pa 'di yin te //
NK079(dzu)002:1591: drug gi 'jig rten phyogs bcu 'das dang da ltar rgyal ba yang //
NK079(dzu)002:1592: gsang ba 'di bsnyen sku lnga lhun gyis grub pa yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1593: de bzhin 'byung dang ma 'ongs 'di yis grub //
NK079(dzu)002:1594: de'i phyir 'di ni gsang chen nges pa'i 'bras bur lam gyur yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1595: rgyal ba sras bcas kun la'ang 'di las nges don
NK079(dzu)002:1596: gzhan mi mnga' //gzhan nas btsal bas rgyal bas kyang
NK079(dzu)002:1598: 'di gtad rgyud kun las ni 'byung ba'i phyag rgya'i
NK079(dzu)002:1599: mchog /shes rab gsum gyis sbyangs pa'i dmig ldan rnams
NK079(dzu)002:1600: kyis gzung // snod ldan ngang tshul bzang la blo brtan pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1601: lus dang longs spyod gtong phod tsam las ma gtogs gzhan du mi sbyin no //
NK079(dzu)002:1602: gal te byin na rmongs 'phyar de nyid srog zad ngan 'gror ltung //
NK079(dzu)002:1603: shin tu gsang ba man ngag snying po'i le'u ste
NK079(dzu)002:1604: bcu gsum pa'o ////de nas dgyes pa chen pos glu
NK079(dzu)002:1605: 'di blangs // glu drug blangs pas sangs rgyas che ba'i yon tan kun rdzogs phyir //
NK079(dzu)002:1606: dang po tshogs chen gnyis su bstan pa dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1607: gnyis pa rdo rje rnam bzhi brjod pa yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1608: gsum pa rdzogs pa rnam pa bzhir grags so //
NK079(dzu)002:1609: bzhi pa las ni mtha' yas bzhi zhes bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1610: lnga pa rdul snyed rnam pa bzhir bstod pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1611: drug pa sku gsung thugs ni rnam pa bzhi //
NK079(dzu)002:1612: nyi shu rtsa bzhi bstod pa'i dkyil 'khor rdzogs //
NK079(dzu)002:1613: mnyes pa'i le'u ste bcu bzhi pa'o ////de nas bde gshegs rgyal po'i rgyal ba bdag po des //
NK079(dzu)002:1614: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor nyid du mngon par 'du mdzod de //
NK079(dzu)002:1615: ci phyir ji ltar btul nas las bsgos mdzad dang gsum //
NK079(dzu)002:1616: ci phyi 'dul mdzad rnam pa gsum yin te //
NK079(dzu)002:1617: khams gsum pa yi rgyu dang rkyen dang 'bras bu'o //
NK079(dzu)002:1618: rgyu ni bdag rtog la sogs rmongs pa'i bar //
NK079(dzu)002:1619: srid pa'i sa bon rtsub mos 'phangs pa rkyen yin te //
NK079(dzu)002:1620: 'bras bu dmyal ba yi dwags srin po gsum //
NK079(dzu)002:1621: ru dra rnam gsum zhes kyang de la bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1622: ji ltar 'dul dbang ngag gis dus 'dul te //
NK079(dzu)002:1623: che mchog nyid 'ang khro bo 'chol ba dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1624: rdo rje zhe sdang dang ni rdo rje srin po dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1625: rdo rje khro bo dang ni 'jigs byed khro bo'o //
NK079(dzu)002:1626: che mchog khro bo'i ting 'dzin snyoms zhugs nas //
NK079(dzu)002:1627: gnyis med mtha' las khro bo 'chol ba bton //
NK079(dzu)002:1628: de ni che mchog dkyil 'khor dang po yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1629: khro bo 'chol bas rdul snyed cho 'phrul ston //
NK079(dzu)002:1630: phyogs bcu'i de wa thams cad 'dul bar mdzad //
NK079(dzu)002:1631: dkyil 'khor gnyis pa zhes ni de la bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1632: de nas che mchog dbus kyi gtsor bsgyur te //
NK079(dzu)002:1633: phyogs bcu'i khro bo 'dus nas rigs bzhir gyur //
NK079(dzu)002:1634: gzungs bcas dregs pa gnon pa'i phrin las mdzad //
NK079(dzu)002:1635: zhe sdang rdo rje zhes bya'i dkyil 'khor gsum pa'o //
NK079(dzu)002:1636: dregs pa nga rgyal ston pa 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK079(dzu)002:1637: de nyid dbu dgu srin por snang bar gyur //
NK079(dzu)002:1638: rdo rje srin pos bsgral nas zhal du stob //
NK079(dzu)002:1639: dbang phyug ma rnams sngags kyis bsdu ba mdzad //
NK079(dzu)002:1640: de ni srin po'i dkyil 'khor bzhi pa'o //
NK079(dzu)002:1641: de nyid khrag 'thung rigs lngar snang byas te //
NK079(dzu)002:1642: dbang phyug ma rnams so so'i sku la 'khril //
NK079(dzu)002:1643: re re las kyang phra men nyi shu'i tshogs bton te //
NK079(dzu)002:1644: rang rang gnas nas stan la 'khod par byas //
NK079(dzu)002:1645: de phyir byi mo zhes kyang de la bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1646: phra men re re la yang tshogs zhes de phyir brjod //
NK079(dzu)002:1647: de nas 'byung mo rang rang gnas su phata kyis 'phangs //
NK079(dzu)002:1648: dbang phyug chen po kun kyang mi gtsang snams su bston //
NK079(dzu)002:1649: snams nas u rtsus phyung ste 'dam 'thung slar dran rnyed //
NK079(dzu)002:1650: de ni dkyil 'khor lnga pa zhes su bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1651: de la 'jig byed dbu ni dgu brgyad pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1652: kun las phyag rgya sprul las 'jigs par ston //
NK079(dzu)002:1653: de tshe 'dul thabs bsam yas tha dad pas //
NK079(dzu)002:1654: phyi nang bdud tshogs thams cad dus gcig btul //
NK079(dzu)002:1655: de ni 'jigs byed ces kyang drug par bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1656: las bsgrol bas ni de dag 'dar byed nas //
NK079(dzu)002:1657: 'bangs su gnas so dkyil 'khor gdan la bzhag /rang
NK079(dzu)002:1658: rang gnas su ma sring bu mo chung ma rnams
NK079(dzu)002:1659: // phul te tshogs kyang khas blangs mna' bor ro //
NK079(dzu)002:1660: grub pa lang+ga'i tshogs su khas 'ches so //
NK079(dzu)002:1661: ma sring bu mo'i tshogs rnams kyis //
NK079(dzu)002:1662: 'khor du 'dus te las kyi dngos grub mnos //
NK079(dzu)002:1663: ming btags lag tu rdo rje byin nas dkyil 'khor phyi rol bkod //
NK079(dzu)002:1664: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor gyi rnam par 'phros pa'i le'u
NK079(dzu)002:1665: ste bco lnga pa'o ////de nas bcom ldan dges pa
NK079(dzu)002:1666: chen pos khros bo'i gsung phyung ba /
NK079(dzu)002:1667: ci'i phyir gang las gang phyung phyung ba'i mthu dang bzhi //
NK079(dzu)002:1668: ci phyir khro tshogs byang chub bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK079(dzu)002:1669: gang las khrag 'thung sku gsung thugs rdo rje las //
NK079(dzu)002:1670: gang phyung lnga bcu rtsa brgyad gsang sngags dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1671: spyan drangs bzhugs dang dngos grub blangs pa dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1672: mchod dang dkyil 'khor bton te rnam drug yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1673: lnga bcu rtsa brgyad khro rgyal yab yum bcu'i //
NK079(dzu)002:1674: ta th+aa ga ta badz+ra rat+na dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1675: pad+ma karma rtsa ba'i snying po ste //
NK079(dzu)002:1676: ma h+aa tsa n+da la sogs las kyi yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1677: dkar mo la sogs sa bon ha brgyad de //
NK079(dzu)002:1678: badz+ra koo ri la sogs rtsa ba'i sngags su bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1679: sid+ha la sogs brgyad kyang de bzhin no //
NK079(dzu)002:1680: dzahmh'u ba ho sgo srung sa bon yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1681: rang rang rigs zhes rtsa ba'i sngags zhes gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1682: phra men nyi shu'i tshogs la mgo dang 'jug nyid du //
NK079(dzu)002:1683: dang h'u phata brgyan te bzlas byas na //
NK079(dzu)002:1684: ci 'dod las rnams thams cad 'grub par 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)002:1685: nyi shu rtsa brgyad b+h+yo yis bskul bar gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1686: e h+ya hi a na ya dzahmh'u bam ho ram gyis spyan yang drangs /
NK079(dzu)002:1687: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya h'u gis 'jug pa nyid du bya /
NK079(dzu)002:1688: dngos grub blang phyir bskul tshig 'di yang brjod //
NK079(dzu)002:1689: dregs pas khro la thugs rje'i khros pas dregs pa ngang gis zhi mdzad pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1690: thugs rje dpal chen rngams pa'i cha lugs 'dzin pa rnams //
NK079(dzu)002:1691: khro rgyal rngams pa'i sku gsung thugs yin phrin las rmad po che /
NK079(dzu)002:1692: dus 'di nyid du rnal 'byor bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK079(dzu)002:1693: badz+ra kro d+ha sa ma ya stam phata hohzhesa pas blang bar bya /
NK079(dzu)002:1694: de nyid khrag 'thung sbyor ba'i brdar yang mkhas pas bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1695: a li u li ta pa ti dam sham roo
NK079(dzu)002:1696: tri kha ram yo gi ni kha hi ho zhes
NK079(dzu)002:1697: mchod par bya / de nyid gnyis med po de bstim pa'i brdar yang mkhas pas bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1698: h'u ha he phata ces snying pos gdon /
NK079(dzu)002:1699: de nyid mkhas la gdon par yang ni rgyal bas gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1700: nus mthus tshig 'bar gang bar che 'bring rnam pa dagu'o //
NK079(dzu)002:1701: khro bo'i sngags kyi le'u ste bcu drug pa'o ////bcom
NK079(dzu)002:1702: 'das dgyes pas nyid kyis dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i phyir
NK079(dzu)002:1703: // 'gro ba'i ched du dkyil 'khor de nyid ched du brjod par mdzad //
NK079(dzu)002:1704: dbyibs rgyan gdan dang mdog dang cha lugs dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1705: chas dang gsung sgra phyag mtshan btsun mo nyid dang 'khor //
NK079(dzu)002:1706: rnam pa 'di bcus 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub //
NK079(dzu)002:1707: dbyibs ni ye shes me 'bar ba yi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1708: mu khyud gru chad sgo bzhi bar khyams gnyis kyis gru bzhi mdzes //
NK079(dzu)002:1709: gnas kyi rgyan mchog thod pa'i phreng ba tshar gsum dbang tshag sgrom //
NK079(dzu)002:1710: sbrul lnga rigs lnga mnga' brnyes dug lnga lhun gyis grub //
NK079(dzu)002:1711: nyi ma gsal bsreg rang bzhin mdzad par bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1712: me yi rang bzhin 'bar ba la ni 'phro ba
NK079(dzu)002:1713: mang po 'khrug /gdan mchog gdul dka' mi 'jigs khyu
NK079(dzu)002:1714: mchog dang // stobs mchog ma he thig le'i klong
NK079(dzu)002:1715: yangs gzig /dpa' gtul za byed stag dang gtum rngams
NK079(dzu)002:1717: dbang phyug che dang dri za gnod sbyin srin po gshin rje so sor gzung //
NK079(dzu)002:1718: de phyir che ba'i che ba dbang phyug kyang ches gnon ces bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1719: sku mdog drag po'i kha dog lngar snang ba //
NK079(dzu)002:1720: nyi shu rtsa lnga drag po'i mdog yin no //
NK079(dzu)002:1721: tshul dgu ldan phyir 'jigs pa'i sku zhes bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1722: cha lugs rnam thar dbu gsum pha rol phyin drug
NK079(dzu)002:1723: phyag /zhabs bzhi bgrod med mthar phyin lam zhes bshad
NK079(dzu)002:1724: // chas ni zhing dang glang chen ko rlon stag sogs sku la gsol //
NK079(dzu)002:1725: thod sbrul nyi mas dbu dang mgul chu phyag zhabs brjid par brgyan //
NK079(dzu)002:1726: gsung sgra h'u phata la sogs 'jigs par bsgrags //
NK079(dzu)002:1727: stong gi 'jig rten la sogs phyag mtshon char ba rnams //
NK079(dzu)002:1728: ces 'dul thabs kyi rang rang lag cha ma nges sna tshogs bsnams //
NK079(dzu)002:1729: btsun mo'i tshogs ni cha lugs yab dang mthun par 'khril //
NK079(dzu)002:1730: de ltar yab yum bcu po che bar brtsis gyur na //
NK079(dzu)002:1731: dbu ni sum cus rnam thar sum cu mtshan pa ste //
NK079(dzu)002:1732: rigs lnga dbyings dang ye shes rnam thar sum cu yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1733: dgu bcu'i spyan gyis nyon mongs dgu bcu'i mtha' la gzigs //
NK079(dzu)002:1734: drug cu'i snyan gyis lta ba bcu drug mtha' gsan cing //
NK079(dzu)002:1735: drug cu'i shangs nas drug cu'i 'dul ba sprul pa 'phro //
NK079(dzu)002:1736: drug cu'i ljags kyis lta ba drug cu'i 'dul thabs 'chad //
NK079(dzu)002:1737: drug cu'i gnas su drug cu'i skur ston pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1738: drug cu'i thugs kyis drug cu'i 'dul thabs mnga' //zhabs
NK079(dzu)002:1739: ni bzhi bcu lam yang bzhi bcu bgrod med dgrol
NK079(dzu)002:1740: // dbyings dang ye shes kyis ni rtag chad mtha' bcom pas //
NK079(dzu)002:1741: lha gnas drug cu rtsa gnyis 'jams zhes mkhas pas bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1742: spyir na bzhi brgya drug cu'i dgongs pa bsam mi khyab //
NK079(dzu)002:1743: bsnams pa rgyan gyi che ba bshad pa yang //
NK079(dzu)002:1744: dbu rgyan dang ni mgur chu gsum gsum ste //
NK079(dzu)002:1745: dpung rgyan dang ni phyag gdub drug drug yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1746: sku la g.yang gzhi ko rlon sham thabs sked bcings bzhi bzhis brgyan pa'o //
NK079(dzu)002:1747: zhabs gdub bzhi yin me ris brgyan pa ste //
NK079(dzu)002:1748: lnga gnyis dag la phyir na nyis brgya bdun cus brgyan //
NK079(dzu)002:1749: de dag mtshan ma'i gnyer gyis ci rigs bshad par bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1750: gnas dang yul skyong slas dang byi mo'i tshogs //
NK079(dzu)002:1751: zhing gi stan dang rang rang lag char bcas //
NK079(dzu)002:1752: ci bgyi zhes te mngag gzhug chas nas gnas //
NK079(dzu)002:1753: de nyid dbu gcig spyan gsum snyan shangs ljags dang ni //
NK079(dzu)002:1754: sku dang thugs dang zhabs ni gnyis gnyis te //
NK079(dzu)002:1755: re re la yang bcu drug cha dang ldan //
NK079(dzu)002:1756: bzhi bcu rtsa brgyad tshogs la brtsis gyur na //
NK079(dzu)002:1757: bdun brgya drug cu rtsa brgyad rdzogs par bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1758: spyir na brgya phrag bcu gnyis dang ni nyi shu rtsa bzhir bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1759: dbu rgyan mgur chu dag ni re re ste //
NK079(dzu)002:1760: dpung rgyan zhabs gdub phyag gdub gnyis gnyis yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1761: g.yang gzhi la sogs lnga po gtso dang mthun //
NK079(dzu)002:1762: de ltar brtsis na drug brgya nyi shu rtsa bzhi yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1763: spyir na rgyan gyi che ba brgyad brgya dang ni dgu bcu bzhi'o //
NK079(dzu)002:1764: de ltar stong phrag gnyis dang brgya dang bco brgyad kyis //
NK079(dzu)002:1765: gdul bya'i dgongs pa bsam yas lhun gyis grub //
NK079(dzu)002:1766: 'gro ba gcig la'ang de kun tshang bas na //
NK079(dzu)002:1767: 'jig rten drug gi phyogs bcu mtha' yas pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1768: 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor yin ces rgyal bas de phyir gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1769: de bas de phyir rtsis las 'das zhes mkhas pas bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1770: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa'i le'u ste bcu bdun
NK079(dzu)002:1771: pa'o ////de nas ston pas mnyes pa'i mchod pa 'gro
NK079(dzu)002:1773: sbyor dang sgrol dang bdud rtsi 'dod yon dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1774: 'bras bu dang ni the tshom bsal ba rnam drug yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1775: sgrol ba bdag gzhan gnyis su med pa ste //
NK079(dzu)002:1776: thog mar bdag nyid mnyam pa'i don rtogs dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1777: brtan par bsgom ste bsgral ces rgyal bas gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1778: gzhan gyi rtog ngan gnyis med blo can gyis //
NK079(dzu)002:1779: ma rtogs sems can snying rjes bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK079(dzu)002:1780: bdag gzhan gnyis med dbyings su gcig par bsgral //
NK079(dzu)002:1781: gnyis med 'khril ba'i lhag sems mnyam sbyor gyis //
NK079(dzu)002:1782: bdag nyid bde myong bde gshegs mchog sbyor yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1783: mnyam pa'i grub rdzas bdud rtsi rnam lnga po //
NK079(dzu)002:1784: bdag dang mnyam pa'i bde gshegs tshogs la 'bul //
NK079(dzu)002:1785: 'dod yon bza' btung bgo dang longs spyod lnga //
NK079(dzu)002:1786: de nyid dkyil 'khor yin te dkyil 'khor tshogs la 'bul //
NK079(dzu)002:1787: 'bras bu rang sems bde gshegs yon tan te //
NK079(dzu)002:1788: lha klu mthu chen gzhan las ga la 'byung //
NK079(dzu)002:1789: de phyir sems nyid las su rang ba'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK079(dzu)002:1790: rang lus phyag rgyar gsal zhing som nyi med gyur na //
NK079(dzu)002:1791: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor dngos grub 'bar ba 'grub //
NK079(dzu)002:1792: de skad brjod pas mchod pa thams cad kun tu khyab //
NK079(dzu)002:1793: mchod sbyin dam pa bstan pa'i le'u ste bco brgyad pa'o ////don rnams yod par bya ba'i phyir //
NK079(dzu)002:1794: dam tshig 'gro ba'i ched du brjod //
NK079(dzu)002:1795: phun sum tshogs pa rnam dag dang ni mnyam nyid dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1796: rtsa dang yan lag nyams skyon yon tan dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1797: grogs ngan spangs dang rang bzhin dbye ba dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1798: dgongs pa'i don dang grub dang yon tan rnams //
NK079(dzu)002:1799: rnam pa bcu gsum gyis ni yang dag bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1800: phun sum tshogs pa bla med theg 'di la //
NK079(dzu)002:1801: nyon mongs spyad kyang 'bras bu tshogs 'gyur te //
NK079(dzu)002:1802: tshogs kun rdzogs pa tshul khrims phun sum tshogs //
NK079(dzu)002:1803: rnam dag bla med mchog gi dam tshig 'dis //
NK079(dzu)002:1804: 'dul dbang sdom pa ji snyed gsungs pa yang //
NK079(dzu)002:1805: 'dir 'dus 'dis gsung ngang du rnam par dag /mnyam nyid ces pa bzhi po ma grub ste //
NK079(dzu)002:1806: don dam yod med dbu mar mi dmigs shing //
NK079(dzu)002:1807: kun rdzob snang ba sgyu ma mig yor tshul yin pas //
NK079(dzu)002:1808: srog dang srog gcod gcad pa ga la yod //
NK079(dzu)002:1809: srog dang skyes bur brtags pa'ang log par brtags //
NK079(dzu)002:1810: bden gnyis dbyer med dbyings su ro gcig pas //
NK079(dzu)002:1811: thams cad rang las sprul te longs spyod de //
NK079(dzu)002:1812: de bas rdzas dang ma byin len dang blang mi dmigs //
NK079(dzu)002:1813: chos kun sgyu ma ming tshig btags kun brdzun //
NK079(dzu)002:1814: brdzun la rdzun spyod brdzun btags ga la yod //
NK079(dzu)002:1815: chags med dbyings la rig pas chags pa dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1816: chags spyod nyid na chags dang chag med chag yul med //
NK079(dzu)002:1817: tshangs par spyod nyid tshangs mchog tshangs chen yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1818: de bas byed spyod thams cad tshogs chen rdzogs par rol //
NK079(dzu)002:1819: rtsa ba rnam lnga bsgrub dang bsrung ba'i dam tshig yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1820: yan lag bcu ni ye nas dag mnyam rtogs pas spyod //
NK079(dzu)002:1821: rtsa ba lnga nyams sangs rgyas rigs med skyon //
NK079(dzu)002:1822: 'dir yang sgrub pa'i log 'gyur phyi ma yid du mi 'ong 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)002:1823: yan lag 'da' dka' 'bras bu med de ngan song ltung rnams nyams //
NK079(dzu)002:1824: yon tan sangs rgyas mnyam thob 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)002:1825: grogs ngan rtsa ba'i dam tshig nyams pa'i 'chal ba
NK079(dzu)002:1826: dag /nyams na myur du gso la mi brtson pa
NK079(dzu)002:1828: skad cig smras pa tsam gyis nyes pa 'go ba yong //
NK079(dzu)002:1829: rang bzhin rdo rje sangs rgyas bdag nyid yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1830: dbye ba rtsa ba'i dam tshig lnga po gcig la yang //
NK079(dzu)002:1831: rang gi mtshan nyid thabs dang rang bzhin med par shes rab gnyis zhes bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1832: gcig la'ang rang rig de la sku gsung yon tan phrin las thugs //
NK079(dzu)002:1833: gzhi dang yan lag de ltar bcu phrag gsum zhes bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1834: de yi steng du gzhi mo sum cu bsnan nas brgya drug cu //
NK079(dzu)002:1835: yan lag bcu po gcig la yang ni rigs lnga ste //
NK079(dzu)002:1836: de las sku gsung thugs te nyi shu 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)002:1837: de ltar spyir na sum brgya drug cur 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)002:1838: dgongs pas 'gro ba'i rnam rtog ji snyed pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1839: de 'dul gnyen por dam tshig de snyed 'phro //
NK079(dzu)002:1840: kun bzang chen po yon tan ji snyed pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1841: bsam yas dam tshig 'dis ni 'grub par gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1842: yon tan dam tshig bsrung ba'i rig 'dzin de //
NK079(dzu)002:1843: srid gsum gtso dang nga yi 'khor gyis bkur //
NK079(dzu)002:1844: sangs rgyas sras mchog dpa' bos spun du dgongs //
NK079(dzu)002:1845: bde gshegs thun mong min pa'i yul du zhugs //
NK079(dzu)002:1846: kun bzang 'jigs med phyag rgya chen por sbyor //
NK079(dzu)002:1847: bde gshegs sbyor dang 'dul thabs bsam yas pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1848: de dag kun kyang rnam dag lhun gyis grub //
NK079(dzu)002:1849: dam tshig nyams kyang gso ru rung zhes bde gshegs gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1850: gzhan yang bsam yas yon tan brjod mi lang //
NK079(dzu)002:1851: de skad brjod pas sangs rgyas nyid du 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)002:1852: dam tshig gi le'u ste bcu dgu pa'o ////de nas bcom ldan bde gshegs dgyes chen pos //
NK079(dzu)002:1853: lhun grub byin gyis rlob par mnyam bzhag gnas //
NK079(dzu)002:1854: rnam pa bzhi yi phrin las 'gro ba'i phyir du brjod //
NK079(dzu)002:1855: thabs kyi bye brag dang ni khyad par phrin las dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1856: phyi nang gsang ba gnas kyi khyad par gsum //
NK079(dzu)002:1857: thabs kyi bye brag so so'i man+dala dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1858: lha yi khyad par dang ni ting 'dzin dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1859: mchod sbyin dang ni rgyu dang gzugs byad dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1860: dgug dang gdab dang tshogs la dbul ba dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1861: phyag rgya dang ni dgongs pa gang yin pas //
NK079(dzu)002:1862: lhag ma byin te rnam pa bcu gnyis yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1863: dkyil 'khor e wa ma ya'i tshogs mchog rnams //
NK079(dzu)002:1864: gru gsum zla gam gru bzhi zlum por bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1865: gtum chen rngams dang gzi brjid lhun chen dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1866: 'du 'phro gzi chen gsal ba'i gzi brjid ni //
NK079(dzu)002:1867: drag dbang rgyas zhi lha yi khyad par yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1868: khro chags dga' ba dwang ba'i ting 'dzin dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1869: de dus 'phags pa mchod cing 'gro tshim bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1870: ling+ga'i rgyu ni bdud rtsi lnga'am zas lnga las //
NK079(dzu)002:1871: gang 'dod gzugs byas snying gar ming bris te //
NK079(dzu)002:1872: de yi rnam par shes pa dgug ste dbab //
NK079(dzu)002:1873: khro dang chags dang nga rgyal dga' 'phro dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1874: lhan ner gsal ba grub pa las bzhi'o //
NK079(dzu)002:1875: dbyibs dang kha dog mtshan ldan rab tu gdab //
NK079(dzu)002:1876: de nyid so so'i tshogs la bstims par dbul //
NK079(dzu)002:1877: der ni lu gu rgyud du 'brel bsdams bcings bskyod bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1878: dgongs pa sangs rgyas sku yang myos 'gas tshig pa dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1879: dgug 'gyur phyir 'breng dbang du gyur pa dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1880: yid bzhin gter gyis nam mkha' 'gengs pa dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1881: gtum chen tams pa'ang mi g.yo lhan ner 'gyur //
NK079(dzu)002:1882: slas dang byi mo bran mo bran du bcas pa la //
NK079(dzu)002:1883: lhag ma byin te gang 'dod de la sgo //
NK079(dzu)002:1884: khyad par phrin las khrag 'thung tshogs rnams kyis //
NK079(dzu)002:1885: bskyod pa'i bro dang phyag rgya gar dang ni //
NK079(dzu)002:1886: snyan pa'i glu blangs sngags kyi tshig rnams kyis //
NK079(dzu)002:1887: ci 'dod la sogs las rnams 'grub par gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1888: zhi rgyas dbang drag phyi nang gsang ba'i gnas //
NK079(dzu)002:1889: ljon shing can dang lcug phran rgyas pa'i tshal //
NK079(dzu)002:1890: shing gcig drung dang mes tshig phyi yi gnas //
NK079(dzu)002:1891: ma rmas pa dang pu tra mang 'phel dang //
NK079(dzu)002:1892: skye rgyud med dang bkra mi shis gsang ba //
NK079(dzu)002:1893: ting 'dzin rnam pa bzhi ni nang gi yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1894: phrin las kyi le'u ste nyi shu pa'o ////de nas bde gshegs nyid kyis ni //
NK079(dzu)002:1895: dkyil 'khor che ba'i glu blangs pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1896: sku gsung thugs dang yon tan phrin kyi //
NK079(dzu)002:1897: rang bzhin spyir bstod pa ste drug yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1898: re re la yang dbye na bzhi bzhi ste //
NK079(dzu)002:1899: che ba nyi shu rtsa bzhir shes par bya //
NK079(dzu)002:1900: de kun las dang rang bzhin mthun dpes bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1901: khro bo la bstod pa'i le'u ste nyi shu gcig pa'o ////de nas bcom ldan dgyes chen pos //
NK079(dzu)002:1902: gsang ba 'di nyid snang bya'i phyir //
NK079(dzu)002:1903: sdug pa kun tu bzang po la //
NK079(dzu)002:1904: bstan pa gzung bar che bar brjod //
NK079(dzu)002:1905: kye kye zhes su bos nas su //
NK079(dzu)002:1906: gsang ba bsdu bar gtad par mdzad //
NK079(dzu)002:1907: phyogs bcu dus bzhi bde gshegs ngo bo la //
NK079(dzu)002:1908: gzung 'dzin spros pa mchis pa'i ngo bor 'khor //
NK079(dzu)002:1909: de nyid bzlog phyir khyad par rim bkod pa //
NK079(dzu)002:1910: gsang ba snying po'i bar du bkod par zad //
NK079(dzu)002:1911: bde gshegs ngo mtshar bsam yas dkyil 'khor kun gyis bshad pa yang //
NK079(dzu)002:1912: 'gro ba'i don du 'gyur zhes rgyal bas bshad //
NK079(dzu)002:1913: de kun nang na bde gshegs thams cad kyi //
NK079(dzu)002:1914: phyag rgya gsang chen snying po mchog tu gsungs //
NK079(dzu)002:1915: mchog 'di rtogs nas 'chad par byed pa'i skyes bu ni //
NK079(dzu)002:1916: rdo rje sems dpa' de nyid yin te gsang ba'i dbang yang rdzogs //
NK079(dzu)002:1917: ci phyir zhe na rgyal ba kun la yang //
NK079(dzu)002:1918: gsang ba 'di las gzhan mi mnga' //yod med sgro skur zhi ba'i gsang ba 'di //
NK079(dzu)002:1919: rgyal ba kun gyi dgongs pa'i klong nas phyung //
NK079(dzu)002:1920: gsang ba'i 'di nyid sus 'dzin de ni nges par lung bstan te //
NK079(dzu)002:1921: rgyal ba'i thugs las skyes pa'i sras mchog yin //
NK079(dzu)002:1922: sangs rgyas sar gnas rig 'dzin de la gsang ba 'di nyid gnas //
NK079(dzu)002:1923: de skad brjod pas rgyal ba thams cad gnyis med don la rab dgyes nas //
NK079(dzu)002:1924: dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid de chos kyi dbyings nyid du //
NK079(dzu)002:1925: stug po bkod pa'i rgyan la thim ste bzhugs //
NK079(dzu)002:1926: yongs su gzung ba'i le'u ste nyi shu rtsa gnyis
NK079(dzu)002:1927: pa'o ////bka' gsang rgyal po thugs kyi yang gsang 'di
NK079(dzu)002:1928: // bde gshegs dgongs rgyud thun mong ma yin pas //
NK079(dzu)002:1929: rtog ge bdag 'dra'i spyod yul ma yin zhing //
NK079(dzu)002:1930: rtsing po'i blo yis dpyad par mi 'os kyang //
NK079(dzu)002:1931: phyi rabs dad pa can la phan gdags phyir //
NK079(dzu)002:1932: mdor bsdus dbye ba'i rim pa 'di brtsams pas //
NK079(dzu)002:1933: tshig don gsang ba ci dang ci 'gal ba //
NK079(dzu)002:1934: rnal 'byor dbang phyug spyi la bzod par gsol //
NK079(dzu)002:1935: thugs kyi sgron ma gsang ba'i 'grel pa 'di //
NK079(dzu)002:1936: lung dang man ngag rigs pas gtan la phab //
NK079(dzu)002:1937: dwangs pa'i blo la rang gzhung rnam phye bas //
NK079(dzu)002:1938: rtogs dka' gsang ba'i theg pa'i don rtogs nas //
NK079(dzu)002:1939: shes dka' gsang ba'i theg pa'i don shes shing //
NK079(dzu)002:1940: gsang sngags rgya mtsho khong du chud par shog /gang
NK079(dzu)002:1941: gis gsang ba'i rgyud 'di rab tu rtogs dka' bas
NK079(dzu)002:1942: // tshig gi sgron mas don gyi gser 'tshol te //
NK079(dzu)002:1943: bde blag tu ni rtogs pa'i bsod nams gang //
NK079(dzu)002:1944: mtha' yas sems can kun gyi thob par shog /
NK079(dzu)002:1945: 'phags pa rtog pa'i rgyal po rdo rje sems dpa'
NK079(dzu)002:1946: sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba le'u stong phrag brgya pa las
NK079(dzu)002:1947: / mtshan nyid dang rgyud thams cad kyi lung gi spyi //
NK079(dzu)002:1948: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi gsang ba //
NK079(dzu)002:1949: gsang ba'i snying po de kho na nyid nges pa las //
NK079(dzu)002:1950: thams cad ma lus par 'phros te 'khor lor bskor
NK079(dzu)002:1951: ba de dag gi 'bras bu mchog gi rgyud kyi
NK079(dzu)002:1952: don bsdus 'grel pa pin+dar+tha ra zhes bya ba /
NK079(dzu)002:1953: rgya gar gyi slob dpon chen po bi ma la mi tras mdzad pa /
NK079(dzu)002:1955: zhus chen gyi lo ts+aa ba rin chen a tsar+ya
NK079(dzu)002:1956: rma rin chen mchog dang gnyag dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa
NK079(dzu)002:1957: ras dpal bsam yas dbu rtse'i steng khang du bsgyur
